repo.name: cython

body:
Adds most of the missing minimum/maximum operations, comparison operations and permutation operations of the algorithm library (<= C++17):

- `minmax`, `minmax_element` (C++11), `clamp` (C++17) and one missing overload of `min/max_element`.
- `equal`, `lexicographical_compare`
- `is_permutation`, `next_permutation`, `prev_permutation`

commit.message: add missing overloads and new methods
ignore apple clang's weird template instantiation bugs
last overload of equal needs at least cpp14

Goals:
 New version scheme: 3.x instead of 0.x.

 Change default for `binding` directive from `False` to `True`.
 Fix some Python compatibility issues (if possible, allowing for breaking changes).

title: Add missing min/max, comparison and permutation operations of C++ algorithm library
